A quick copy paste guide for my preferences 

Update system:
su root
sudo apt update
sudo apt upgrade
sudo apt install visudo

- setup user privileges

Firewall:
sudo apt install ufw
sudo ufw default deny incoming
sudo ufw default allow outgoing
sudo ufw enable


Setup Bluetooth:
sudo apt install bluetooth bluez
sudo systemctl enable bluetooth
sudo systemctl start bluetooth


Gnome desktop extensions:
sudo apt install gnome-extension-freon
sudo apt install gnome-extension-dash-to-dock
sudo apt install gnome-extension-system-monitor


Reboot
